\n            </h2><div class=\"about__box-author\">\n            \n              <div class=\"about__box-text\">\n                \n                  <div class=\"about__box-name rte large-font\">\n                    <p>The Founders,</p><p>Pavel &amp; Benny</p>\n                  </div>\n                \n              </div>\n            \n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about_item\"><div class=\"about__subtitle\">\n              It all began with a simple idea: to combine timeless design with practical functionality. Starting as a small studio creating handcrafted sketchbooks, planners, and accessories, the focus was always on quality, attention to detail, and thoughtful design. Over the years, these products have found their way into desks, offices, and creative spaces everywhere, helping people organize their days, capture ideas, and turn inspiration into reality.\n            </div></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n</section>"
